pected to increase in the coming years as up to 50,000 new residents move into the area as part of the Broadway plan.\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Demand\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3061}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming years\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 50,000 new residents\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"the Broadway plan\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The school board forecasts Simon Fraser Elementary will be at 238 per cent capacity by 2029.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fraser_River\", \"score\": 0.9999998985313192, \"rank\": 1.0146876314213273e-07, \"text\": \"Fraser\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fraser_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fraser_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The school board\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"238 per cent capacity\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more than a decade a new Olympic Village school has been at the top of the Vancouver school district's annual capital plan funding submissions to the province.\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3363, \"end\": 3372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.076344763656892e-20, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than a decade\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"a new Olympic Village school\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"the province\", \"from\